#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:1
msgid "Clinical Registers"
msgstr "Registres cliniques"

#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:4
msgid ""
"Resthome's clinical registers — falls, pressure ulcers (Braden), wounds, "
"pain, restraint, nutrition (MNA), continence, mobility, cognition."
msgstr ""
"Les registres cliniques de Resthome — chutes, escarres (Braden), plaies, "
"douleur, contention, nutrition (MNA), continence, mobilité, cognition."

#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:7
msgid ""
"**Clinical registers** structure the monitoring of risks and geriatric "
"assessments. Each register groups together the assessments of a single "
"theme, over time, for each resident."
msgstr ""
"Les **registres cliniques** structurent le suivi des risques et des "
"évaluations gériatriques. Chaque registre regroupe les évaluations d'un même"
" thème, dans le temps, pour chaque résident."

#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:11
msgid "Available registers"
msgstr "Les registres disponibles"

